column5: This specialty boat was released just in time for the 2018 N/W Ontario walleye opener.
And now the 5th time I've seen it posted here. Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk

I want one,...how much? Are the track and skies hydraulically retractable? Can the track be used in conjunction with the boat motor for extra propulsion and can the skies function as a hydrofoil for high speed aqua travel? This design looks like a winner!
